class=\"text-2xl\">🔄</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Workflow</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">多步骤任务编排</div></div></a><a class=\"group flex items-center gap-4 px-4 py-4 rounded-xl transition-all duration-200 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/knowledge\"><span class=\"text-2xl\">🗃️</span><div class=\"flex-1 min-w-0\"><div class=\"font-medium text-gray-700 group-hover:text-gray-900\">Knowledge</div><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400 truncate mt-0.5\">企业知识智能检索</div></div></a></div></nav><div class=\"shrink-0 p-4 border-t border-gray-100 bg-white\"><div class=\"text-sm text-gray-400\"><div>版本 v1.0.0</div><div class=\"mt-1\">© 2026 AI Tools Center</div></div></div></aside><main class=\"flex-1 ml-72\"><div class=\"p-8\"><nav class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6\"><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn\">学院</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><a class=\"hover:text-gray-700 transition-colors\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\">架构师路径</a><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg><span class=\"text-gray-900 font-medium\">Agent 开发</span></nav><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-500 rounded-2xl p-8 text-white mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-4 mb-4\"><span class=\"text-4xl\"></span><div><h1 class=\"text-2xl font-bold\">Agent 开发</h1><p class=\"text-white/80\">多 Agent 协作系统</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-6 text-white/80 text-sm\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 8v4l3 3m6-3a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>预计 <!-- -->100分钟</span></div><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2\"><svg class=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4m6 2a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0z\"></path></svg><span>架构师路径</span></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-4 mb-8\"><div class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-sm\"><span class=\"text-gray-500\">难度选择：</span><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/beginner\">入门路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-gray-100 text-gray-600 hover:bg-gray-200\" href=\"/learn/agent/developer\">开发者路径</a><a class=\"px-3 py-1.5 rounded-lg transition-colors bg-blue-600 text-white\" href=\"/learn/agent/architect\">架构师路径</a></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-xl border border-gray-200 p-8\"><div class=\"prose prose-gray max-w-none\"><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">1</span>协作模式</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-3\"><div class=\"p-3 bg-purple-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">层级式（Hierarchical）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">主 Agent 协调子 Agent，职责清晰</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">项目经理 Agent → {开发Agent, 测试Agent, 文档Agent}</div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-blue-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">对等式（Peer-to-Peer）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">Agent 平等协作，互相交流信息</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">专家Agent A ↔→ 专家Agent B ↔→ 专家Agent C（讨论达成共识）</div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-green-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">竞争式（Competitive）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">多个 Agent 独立执行，选择最优结果</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">写作Agent1, 2, 3 各自生成文案 → 评分 → 选择最佳</div></div><div class=\"p-3 bg-orange-50 rounded-lg\"><h5 class=\"font-semibold mb-2\">流水线式（Pipeline）</h5><p class=\"text-sm text-gray-600 mb-2\">按顺序处理，每个 Agent 负责一个阶段</p><div class=\"bg-white p-2 rounded border text-xs\">数据采集Agent → 清洗Agent → 分析Agent → 报告Agent</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-8 last:mb-0\"><h2 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4 flex items-center gap-2\"><span class=\"w-8 h-8 rounded-lg bg-purple-50 flex items-center justify-center text-sm\">2</span>通信与协调</h2><div class=\"text-gray-600 leading-relaxed space-y-4\"><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded-lg\"><h4 class=\"font-semibold mb-3\">标准化消息协议</h4><div class=\"font-mono text-xs\"><pre>{\n  &quot;type&quot;: &quot;request/response/notify/error&quot;,\n  &quot;from&quot;: &quot;agent_id&quot;,\n  &quot;to&quot;: &quot;agent_id&quot;,\n  &quot;timestamp&quot;: &quot;2024-03-07T15:30:00Z&quot;,\n  &quot;content&quot;: { ... },\n  &quot;correlation_id&quot;: &quot;uuid-for-tracing&quot;\n}</pre></div></div><div class=\"space-y-2 text-sm\"><p><strong>关键机制：</strong></p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-5 space-y-1\"><li>消息总线：集中式消息队列（RabbitMQ/Kafka）</li><li>事件驱动：Agent 订阅/发布事件</li><li>状态管理：共享状态或事件总线同步</li><li>冲突解决：协商、投票、仲裁机制</li></ul></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mt-8 flex items-center justify-between\"><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn/path/architect\"><svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M15 19l-7-7 7-7\"></path></svg>返回<!-- -->架构师路径</a><a class=\"flex items-center gap-2 text-gray-600 hover:text-blue-600 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-gray-50\" href=\"/learn\">返回学院<svg class=\"w-5 h-5\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M9 5l7 7-7 7\"></path></svg></a></div></div><!--$--><!--/$--></main></div></div><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/0j6kpnbwgrhei.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[30824,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"Providers\\\"]\\n3:I[87161,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[40715,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n5:I[78691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n6:I[30470,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pe7_.ico216u.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n8:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"OutletBoundary\\\"]\\n9:\\\"$Sreact.suspense\\\"\\nc:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"ViewportBoundary\\\"]\\ne:I[98544,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"MetadataBoundary\\\"]\\n10:I[92691,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0~gz256ffq795.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0pk5qoo78d3co.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\",1]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0.6dsdn7g3rv..css\\\",\\\"style\\\"]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/static/media/797e433ab948586e-s.p.0.q-h669a_dqa.woff2\\\",\\\"font\\\",{\\\"crossOrigin\\\":\\\"\\\",\\\"type\\\":\\\"font/woff2\\\"}]\\n:HL[\\\"/_next/stat